N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4603.6 - Distribution of copies by clerk

State Regulations

The clerk of the municipality shall prepare the license
in quadruplicate, issue the original to the licensee, retain a copy, forward a
copy to the local law enforcement agency and forward a copy to the commission
at least five days prior to the holding of the first game
authorized. Notes
